---
import Base from '../../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="AegisTrans Support — AegisRD" description="Support for AegisTrans sign-in, transfers, subscriptions, and accounts." altPath="/aegistrans/support" active="aegistrans">
  <section class="hero" style="min-height:34vh"><div class="hero-content"><div class="hero-badge">AEGISTRANS · SUPPORT</div><h1 style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)">AegisTrans Support</h1><p>Help with sign-in, peer-to-peer transfers, subscriptions, and accounts.</p></div></section>
  <section class="problem"><div class="container support-copy">
    <h2>Try these first</h2>
    <ol><li>Confirm both devices use the same AegisTrans account and update both apps.</li><li>Keep both apps open and retry on a normal home Wi-Fi or mobile network.</li><li>Corporate, campus, CGNAT, or symmetric-NAT networks may block direct connections; AegisTrans does not use a TURN relay.</li></ol>
    <h2>Purchases and subscriptions</h2>
    <p>After reinstalling or changing devices, choose Restore Purchases on the Upgrade Pro screen. Manage subscriptions through <a href="https://apps.apple.com/account/subscriptions">Apple</a> or <a href="https://play.google.com/store/account/subscriptions?package=com.aegisrd.aegistrans">Google Play</a>. Refunds are handled by the store that processed the payment.</p>
    <h2>Account and privacy</h2>
    <p>Delete your account under Settings → Danger zone, or use the <a href="/en/aegistrans/delete-account">web deletion request</a>. See the <a href="/en/aegistrans/terms">AegisTrans Terms</a> and <a href="https://trans.aegisrd.com/privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
    <h2>Contact us</h2>
    <p>Email <a href="mailto:support@aegisrd.com">support@aegisrd.com</a> with the platform, app version, approximate time, and a screenshot. Do not send passwords, full purchase credentials, private files, or other sensitive content.</p>
  </div></section>
</Base>
<style>.support-copy{max-width:820px;line-height:1.9}.support-copy h2{color:var(--text-primary);font-size:1.3rem;margin:2.2rem 0 .6rem}.support-copy p,.support-copy li{color:var(--text-secondary)}.support-copy a{color:var(--accent);text-decoration:underline}</style>
